      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "When your file has more lines than will fit on one screen, you can use"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "the scroll commands UP and DOWN to see other portions of the file."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "When the data is wider than the screen, you can scroll LEFT and RIGHT."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "To change the number of lines or columns that are scrolled each time"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "you issue a scrolling command, change the scroll amount field."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "The following topics may be selected by number:"
      },
